      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJOR SOKO (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 5 (18.41). Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. The form out of her last race has been franked. Well placed and can measure up. FANTASIA QUEEN (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.49) in a Mix 1/2/3 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from 10 starts. Likely to play a prominent role. SHOT OF FAITH (8) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (18.66) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Solid record here winning five races. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to be in the finish again. CRIMSON DYNAMO (6) placed last time and cannot be ignored.",
